text: It's fine that you think this.
In the worst Libertarian disgrace yet, Noah Smith is apologizing to them. noahpinion.blog/p/i-owe-the-…
"For those too squeamish or skeptical to invoke the deity, I can produce a mathematical explanation ..." city-journal.org/article/don…
... proceeds to invoke The Invisible Hands.
Doesn't the number need to be ~5 times this level just to seriously deal with the Biden-era catastrophe?

You might be underestimating progressive willingness to accept the fully-extrapolated version of their proposals. Their only likely reluctance to go for immediate pan-euthanasianism is that it expends too much grievance politics in one gulp.
If we weren't drenched in miracles to the point of utter numbness we'd be fainting through sheer dark bliss at this.
